
Overview of verb socialize

The verb socialize has 4 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                      
1. (1) socialize, socialise -- (take part in social activities; interact with others; "He never socializes with his colleagues"; "The old man hates to socialize")
2. socialize, socialise -- (train for a social environment; "The children must be properly socialized")
3. socialize, socialise -- (prepare for social life; "Children have to be socialized in school")
4. socialize, socialise -- (make conform to socialist ideas and philosophies; "Health care should be socialized!")
